<plot>Film Threat magazine creator/editor, and book author Chris Gore hosts "Festival Pass with Chris Gore" taking viewers to film festivals all over the world. This episode features interviews with Harvey Pekar ("American Splendor"), Bob Odenkirk ("Melvin Goes to Dinner"), William H. Macy ("The Cooler"), Paul Rudd ("The Shape of Things") Dustin Hoffman ("Confidence"), Holly Hunter and Sundance Festival founder Robert Redford.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?192928</url></doc>
